title: NASA research jet makes fiery 'wheels-up landing' after experiencing mechanical issue (video)
description: One of NASA's high-altitude WB-57 research jet made a fiery wheels-up landing on Tuesday (Jan. 27) after a mechanical issue prevented it from lowering its landing gear.
